The paper discusses a system for probabilistic query processing and data cleaning, which falls under the domain of databases (cs.DB). The use of probabilistic techniques also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data science (cs.DS). The paper also describes a GUI for interactive exploration, which falls under human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and discusses optimizations for scalability, which is relevant to software engineering (cs.SE).
